title: J.River MC18.0.206 + patch
description:
J.river Media Center 18.0.206 + patch (working!!!)

1.Install J.River WITH INTERNET CONNECTION DISABLED!!!!

2.on first launch go to HELP/UPDATE CHANNELS AND SELECT "disable automatic updates"

3.close the application

4.Copy patch.exe to install directory & launch it As Administrator,(not sure about date to choose but i choose something in 2014)click on the skull to patch!
